title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Dec 30 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Dec 30 2021
description:
EIB Guest Host Michael Berry, "The Czar of Talk" from NewsRadio 740 KTRH in Houston, debriefed Jack Posobiec on why the Ghislaine Maxwell guilty verdict matters. Plus, a look back at those we lost in 2021. Michael takes your calls, including from a woman whose brother turned her on to conservatism before his passing in August.
